---
import Mascot from '../Mascot.astro';
---
<section class="slide slide-ww01">
  <div class="content">
    <h2 class="title">¿Qué es un Web Worker?</h2>

    <div class="main-grid">
      <div class="svg-box">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 320 200" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
             aria-label="Diagrama de un Web Worker corriendo en paralelo al hilo principal">
          <defs>
            <marker id="ww01-arrow" markerWidth="7" markerHeight="7" refX="6" refY="3.5" orient="auto">
              <path d="M0,0 L7,3.5 L0,7 Z" fill="#38BDF8"/>
            </marker>
            <marker id="ww01-arrow-pink" markerWidth="7" markerHeight="7" refX="6" refY="3.5" orient="auto">
              <path d="M0,0 L7,3.5 L0,7 Z" fill="#F472B6"/>
            </marker>
          </defs>

          <!-- Navegador (contenedor) -->
          <rect x="10" y="10" width="300" height="180" rx="10" fill="#1E293B" stroke="#475569" stroke-width="1.5"/>
          <text x="160" y="28" text-anchor="middle" fill="#94A3B8" font-size="9" font-weight="600">NAVEGADOR</text>

          <!-- Main Thread -->
          <rect x="25" y="38" width="120" height="140" rx="7" fill="#0C2A3F" stroke="#38BDF8" stroke-width="2"/>
          <text x="85" y="56" text-anchor="middle" fill="#38BDF8" font-size="9" font-weight="700">MAIN THREAD</text>
          <rect x="35" y="64" width="100" height="18" rx="4" fill="#1D3461" stroke="#3B82F6" stroke-width="1"/>
          <text x="85" y="77" text-anchor="middle" fill="#93C5FD" font-size="8" font-family="monospace">DOM</text>
          <rect x="35" y="88" width="100" height="18" rx="4" fill="#1D3461" stroke="#3B82F6" stroke-width="1"/>
          <text x="85" y="101" text-anchor="middle" fill="#93C5FD" font-size="8" font-family="monospace">UI Events</text>
          <rect x="35" y="112" width="100" height="18" rx="4" fill="#1D3461" stroke="#3B82F6" stroke-width="1"/>
          <text x="85" y="125" text-anchor="middle" fill="#93C5FD" font-size="8" font-family="monospace">Event Loop</text>
          <!-- Indicador activo -->
          <circle cx="85" cy="155" r="6" fill="#10B981" class="pulse-dot"/>
          <text x="97" y="159" fill="#6EE7B7" font-size="8">activo</text>

          <!-- Flechas de mensajes -->
          <path d="M147 100 L173 100" stroke="#38BDF8" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="4,3" marker-end="url(#ww01-arrow)" class="msg-right"/>
          <path d="M173 115 L147 115" stroke="#F472B6" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="4,3" marker-end="url(#ww01-arrow-pink)" class="msg-left"/>
          <text x="160" y="97" text-anchor="middle" fill="#38BDF8" font-size="7">postMessage</text>
          <text x="160" y="128" text-anchor="middle" fill="#F472B6" font-size="7">message</text>

          <!-- Worker Thread -->
          <rect x="175" y="38" width="120" height="140" rx="7" fill="#3D0A24" stroke="#F472B6" stroke-width="2"/>
          <text x="235" y="56" text-anchor="middle" fill="#F472B6" font-size="9" font-weight="700">WEB WORKER</text>
          <rect x="185" y="64" width="100" height="18" rx="4" fill="#5a1035" stroke="#F472B6" stroke-width="1"/>
          <text x="235" y="77" text-anchor="middle" fill="#FBCFE8" font-size="8" font-family="monospace">JS puro</text>
          <rect x="185" y="88" width="100" height="18" rx="4" fill="#5a1035" stroke="#F472B6" stroke-width="1"/>
          <text x="235" y="101" text-anchor="middle" fill="#FBCFE8" font-size="8" font-family="monospace">Sin DOM</text>
          <rect x="185" y="112" width="100" height="18" rx="4" fill="#5a1035" stroke="#F472B6" stroke-width="1"/>
          <text x="235" y="125" text-anchor="middle" fill="#FBCFE8" font-size="8" font-family="monospace">Hilo propio</text>
          <!-- Indicador activo -->
          <circle cx="235" cy="155" r="6" fill="#F472B6" class="pulse-dot-pink"/>
          <text x="247" y="159" fill="#FBCFE8" font-size="8">activo</text>
        </svg>
      </div>

      <div class="explanation">
        <div class="definition-card">
          <p>
            Un <strong>Web Worker</strong> es un script JavaScript que el navegador ejecuta
            en un <strong>hilo separado</strong>, en paralelo al hilo principal.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="points">
          <div class="point">
            <span class="point-icon" style="background:#0C2A3F; color:#38BDF8;">🧵</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Hilo propio</strong>
              <p>Corre en paralelo real, no intercalado. El navegador le asigna un hilo del sistema operativo.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="point">
            <span class="point-icon" style="background:#3D0A24; color:#F472B6;">🚫</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Sin acceso al DOM</strong>
              <p>No puede tocar la interfaz directamente. Se comunica con el hilo principal por mensajes.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="point">
            <span class="point-icon" style="background:#064E3B; color:#10B981;">⚡</span>
            <div>
              <strong>UI siempre fluida</strong>
              <p>Las tareas pesadas se delegan al worker, el hilo principal sigue respondiendo al usuario.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="types-note">
          <span class="types-label">3 tipos de Workers</span>
          <div class="types-list">
            <div class="type-row active">
              <span class="type-name">Dedicated <span class="type-sub">← este curso</span></span>
              <span class="type-desc">Un worker exclusivo para un script. El más común.</span>
            </div>
            <div class="type-row">
              <span class="type-name">Shared</span>
              <span class="type-desc">Compartido entre múltiples scripts o pestañas.</span>
            </div>
            <div class="type-row">
              <span class="type-name">Service</span>
              <span class="type-desc">Intercepta red, habilita offline y PWAs.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <Mascot message="¡Un Web Worker es como contratar a un asistente! Tú sigues atendiendo clientes mientras él hace el trabajo pesado." mood="excited" position="top-left" />
</section>

<style>
  .slide-ww01 {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    height: 100%;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 70% 30%, #0C2A3F 0%, var(--color-bg) 65%);
  }

  .content {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 880px;
    padding: var(--space-8);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-6);
  }

  .title {
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    font-weight: 800;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-main-thread, #38BDF8), var(--color-worker-thread, #F472B6));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .main-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.2fr;
    gap: var(--space-6);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .svg-box {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: var(--space-4);
  }

  .svg-box svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
  }

  .explanation {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-4);
  }

  .definition-card {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: var(--space-4);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .definition-card strong {
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .points {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-3);
  }

  .point {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: var(--space-3) var(--space-4);
  }

  .point-icon {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .point strong {
    display: block;
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    margin-bottom: 2px;
  }

  .point p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .types-note {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: var(--space-3) var(--space-4);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-2);
  }

  .types-label {
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .types-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-2);
  }

  .type-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    padding: var(--space-2) var(--space-3);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    background: var(--color-surface-2);
  }

  .type-row.active {
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-accent) 8%, transparent);
  }

  .type-name {
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    white-space: nowrap;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    min-width: 120px;
  }

  .type-row.active .type-name {
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .type-sub {
    opacity: 0.7;
    font-size: 0.85em;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .type-desc {
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  /* Animaciones SVG */
  @keyframes pulse-green {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; r: 6; }
    50%       { opacity: 0.5; r: 8; }
  }
  @keyframes pulse-pink {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; r: 6; }
    50%       { opacity: 0.5; r: 8; }
  }
  @keyframes msg-slide-right {
    0%, 40%  { opacity: 0; transform: translateX(-8px); }
    50%, 90% { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(0); }
    100%     { opacity: 0; transform: translateX(8px); }
  }
  @keyframes msg-slide-left {
    0%, 40%  { opacity: 0; transform: translateX(8px); }
    50%, 90% { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(0); }
    100%     { opacity: 0; transform: translateX(-8px); }
  }

  .pulse-dot      { animation: pulse-green 2s ease-in-out infinite; }
  .pulse-dot-pink { animation: pulse-pink  2s ease-in-out infinite; animation-delay: 0.5s; }
  .msg-right      { animation: msg-slide-right 3s ease-in-out infinite; }
  .msg-left       { animation: msg-slide-left  3s ease-in-out infinite; animation-delay: 1.5s; }
</style>
